    <title>Escrow, Appraisal, and Mortgage Servicing Improvements Act</title>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require escrows for certain mortgage loans, to improve mortgage servicing, to promote sustainable homeownership opportunities, to enhance appraisal quality and standards, to better appraisal oversight, to mitigate appraiser pressure, and for other purposes.</title>
